  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Lift high the cross, the love of Christ proclaim, Till all the world adore His sacred Name. Come, brethren, follow where our Captain trod, our King victorious, Christ the Son of God.",
    "v2": "Lift high the cross, the love of Christ proclaim, Till all the world adore His sacred Name. Led on their way by this triumphant sign, The hosts of God in conquering ranks combine.",
    "v3": "Lift high the cross, the love of Christ proclaim, Till all the world adore His sacred Name. Each newborn servant of the Crucified Bears on the brow the seal of Him Who died.",
    "v4": "Lift high the cross, the love of Christ proclaim, Till all the world adore His sacred Name. This is the sign which Satan&#39;s legions fear and angels veil their faces to revere.",
    "v5": "Lift high the cross, the love of Christ proclaim, Till all the world adore His sacred Name. Saved by this Cross whereon their Lord was slain, the sons of Adam their lost home regain."
  },
